%% RHOAI 3.5-ea.2 — Workflow 2: Data Science Pipeline Execution
%% Generated from PLATFORM.md by Claude Opus 4.6 on 2026-06-22

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard<br/>Web Console
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Auth Sidecar :8443
    participant DSPApi as DSP API Server<br/>REST :8888 · gRPC :8887
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>Pipeline Metadata
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>gRPC :8080
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>workflow-controller
    participant StepPod as Pipeline Step Pod<br/>driver + launcher
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>Artifacts
    participant PersAgent as Persistence Agent<br/>Status Sync

    Note over User,PersAgent: Workflow 2 — Data Science Pipeline Execution

    %% Step 1: Submit pipeline run
    User->>Dashboard: Navigate to pipeline runs
    Dashboard->>KRBAC: Submit pipeline run request<br/>(HTTPS :8443)
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Validate user permissions
    KRBAC->>DSPApi: Forward authorized request<br/>(REST :8888)

    %% Step 2: Persist pipeline definition
    DSPApi->>MariaDB: Persist pipeline definition<br/>and run metadata (:3306)
    DSPApi->>MLMD: Record artifacts in<br/>ML Metadata (gRPC :8080)
    DSPApi->>Argo: Create Workflow CR<br/>from pipeline DAG

    %% Step 3: Argo schedules pipeline steps
    Argo->>Argo: Parse DAG, resolve<br/>step dependencies
    Argo->>StepPod: Schedule step pod<br/>with argoexec sidecar
    Note over StepPod: Pod contains:<br/>ml-pipeline-driver (input resolution)<br/>launcher (artifact staging)<br/>argoexec (lifecycle mgmt)

    %% Step 4: Execute pipeline step
    StepPod->>MLMD: Driver resolves inputs<br/>from ML Metadata
    MLMD-->>StepPod: Input artifact locations
    StepPod->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>(HTTPS, AWS IAM)
    S3-->>StepPod: Artifact data
    StepPod->>StepPod: Execute user code<br/>(training, preprocessing, etc.)
    StepPod->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>(model, metrics, logs)
    StepPod->>MLMD: Record output artifacts<br/>and execution metadata

    %% Step 5: Status sync
    PersAgent->>Argo: Watch Workflow status changes
    Argo-->>PersAgent: Step completed / failed
    PersAgent->>DSPApi: Sync run and task status<br/>back to database
    DSPApi->>MariaDB: Update run status

    %% Step 6: User monitors progress
    User->>Dashboard: Check pipeline run status
    Dashboard->>KRBAC: Poll DSP API
    KRBAC->>DSPApi: Get run status
    DSPApi->>MariaDB: Query run metadata
    MariaDB-->>DSPApi: Run status + step results
    DSPApi-->>Dashboard: Pipeline execution graph<br/>and artifact outputs
    Dashboard-->>User: Display DAG progress,<br/>step logs, output artifacts
